title: The Inspector Part Deux (vol. 2) - Pink Panther Classic Cartoon
description:
This is a full, uncompressed rip of the Region 1 DVD of "The Inspector, Part Deux." MGM put "The Pink Panther Classic Cartoon Collection" out of print after canceling this volume's individual release; the only way to get your hands on it was to buy some large ass collections for quite a few dollars. So I'm putting it back in print AND giving it the individual release it should've been given. It should work in any region.

I never realized how much I like Sgt. Deux-Deux until he stopped appearing.
